list.name: Changes
list.comment:
New Features:
GlobalMute -> With /globalmute; /chatmute or /mutechat you can disable the chat for everyone that don't have the Permission "yvtils.ba.bypass.mutechat".
AFKDamageKick -> With /afkdamage you can toggle the automatic kick when you get Damage, but you don't allowed to move to much otherwise you will get kicked and the Setting will disabled. When you get Damage you will get kicked and the Setting get disabled. -> Required Permission: "yvtils.ba.command.afkdamage"
Config has new Options. -> Version 8

task.summary: With this Update the /seed Command got Blocked for all Players without a Permission nad give them a Error Message. Players with the Permission must add a Argument which they can get when they use /seed! You can disable this Function in the config.yml. That means it has a new Version.

Deutsch: Plugin Update auf die Minecraft Version 1.18
English: Updated the Plugin for the Minecraft Version 1.18

At this Time this Version is available, you all can have the EVENT-PREMIUM-KEY without me giving it to you.
At the Moment no Premium Features are available, but soon there will come some.
The Download for this Version is available until 01.01.2022 or I forgot to upload a new version then it's no longer aviable.
